parameters: Lutecia: "(No good... At this rate... But... I'm losing strength...)"
Boy: "Ouch, ouch, ouch... Huh? Who are you? Why are you crying?"
Boy: "It's okay... don't be so scared... I'll protect you."
Boy: "I won't let you... lay a finger... on this girl..."
Lutecia: "(No way... this boy... he shouldn't be able to move...)"
Boy: "It's okay... I will... protect you..."
Lutecia: "(Please!... Somehow... return to me, strength!)"
So that's it... that's what happened...
